<HEADLINE> First Kowloon-Beijing Through Train Arrives </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, May 20 (Xinhua) -- The first through passenger train
from Kowloon to Beijing arrived here tonight.
</P>
<P>
