</P>
<P>
for childern with special needs to create equal opportunities
for them to have access to basic education and related services.
</P>
<P>
They also include educational development to support
educational institutions to improve their quality, equity and
relevance of education in both formal and non-formal education
training through the provision of management, planning and
administrative training.
</P>
<P>
According to the press release, the Finnish government
extended aid to Ethiopia amounting to 1 billion Birr (about 150
million U.S,Dollars) during the last 28 years. 
