<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, May 20 (Xinhua) -- Two French businessmen were killed
this afternoon by two men wearing military uniforms in a factory
at the periphery of the central town of Kinshasa, the Agence
France-Presse (AFP) quoted a reliable source as saying.
</P>
<P>
The two men, who were visiting the factory, were stopped by the
gunmen at the gate of the factory, conducted to an office of the
factory building, and shot dead as soon as they entered the room,
