official contact with Israel when it recognizes an independent
Palestinian state with Jerusalem as its capital, Antara news
agency reported today.
</P>
<P>
Abdulrahman said the Palestinians would take the recent Madrid
agreement as the foundation for all future negotiations with
Israel.
