<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, May 21 (Xinhua) -- Philippine Defense Secretary Renato
de Villa will step down from his post next month to join the
ruling party Lakas-NUCD in preparation for his presidential bid,
local newspaper The Manila Chronicle reported today.
</P>
