<HEADLINE> Kazakhstan Unity Party Satisfied With Visit to China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ALMA ATA, May 20 (Xinhua) -- Kazakhstan's Party of National
Unity (PNU) is satisfied with its delegation's recent visit to
China, the party's Vice Chairman S. Diachenko said here.
