relations between the two parties and the two countries on
the basis of the Five Principles of Peaceful Coexistence.
</P>
<P>
The delegation were also impressed by China's achievements in
economic reform, with the country reporting an annual average
increase in gross domestic product of 11 percent, said the
article.
</P>
<P>
The PNU, which was formed in 1993, supports reforms in
Kazakhstan. 
</P>
