<HEADLINE> Australia Beats United States at World Team Cup </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BONN, May 20 (Xinhua) -- World Top-ranked doubles team Mark
Woodforde and Todd Woodbridge gave Australia an surprise win over
the United States at the World Team Cup in Duesseldorf, Germany,
on Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
