</P>
<P>
-- The All-China Federation of Industry and Commerce and the
China Democratic National Construction Association held a forum
here Tuesday to mark the 100th anniversary of the birth of Hu
Zi'ang, a well-known democratic patriot in modern China.
</P>
<P>
-- The State Council and the Central Military Commission
Tuesday sent a telegram of congratulations to those who have
contributed to the recent successful launching of the newly
developed Dongfanghong-3 communications satellite.
</P>
<P>
